{"tid":1216392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日14號 星期五 立法會會議取消","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:32:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b22c6cfdcf3e4f580f1cde44c805e2566eb9e6cc","tid":1216392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:58:35.000Z","msg":"聽日14號 星期五 立法會會議取消<br />\n<br />\n立法會會議不會在明天舉行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《議事規則》第14(3)條，立法會主席決定原訂於2019年6月12日舉行的立法會會議將不會在明天(6月14日)舉行。當立法會主席決定有關會議的舉行時間，將再作通知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年6月13日(星期四)法會會議不會在明天舉行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《議事規則》第14(3)條，立法會主席決定原訂於2019年6月12日舉行的立法會會議將不會在明天(6月14日)舉行。當立法會主席決定有關會議的舉行時間，將再作通知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年6月13日(星期四)"},{"pid":"b51bb0df11d78f634b218e008c0d0b01c8b40dbc","tid":1216392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a5d788aeba4c0f65e54c526b77cfdf5ba3b6ffa","tid":1216392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/press/pr20190613-3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fpress%2Fpr20190613-3.html&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=86c4697c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/press/pr20190613-3.html</a>"},{"pid":"16940f3c48533fdee52583e3c890c7bf254c43f5","tid":1216392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5d788aeba4c0f65e54c526b77cfdf5ba3b6ffa","tid":1216392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/press/pr20190613-3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fpress%2Fpr20190613-3.html&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=86c4697c\" data-auto-link target=\"